Subject: SOP Fiber FPGA Bridge Realization

Description: SOP-HG event record for defining the hardware bridge where speed is frame-rate specific and bandwidth is limited by fiber capacity and FPGA routing width.

@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\SOPFiberFPGABridge.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-24_sop_fiber_fpga_bridge\Dictated_SOP_Fiber_FPGA_Bridge_Source.sop
